310-278-4232

.
Over The Rainbow now open on weekends 🌈
.

Tag your pictures on our Instagram using The Rainbow Bar And Grill location setting 📸
.
.

Monday - Friday 11AM - 7PM

TUESDAY 11am - 2am

9015 Sunset Blvd.
West Hollywood.
California 90069.

.

.

.

Like our page ~ @overthestrip 
And book your stay at our Airbnb! 
To Book a stay go to:
http://overthestrip.com

Cheers! 🥃🥂🍕🍻
